com.vmware.vcenter.namespaces

Interface InstancesTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Instances
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InstancesStub

    public interface InstancesTypes
    The Instances interface provides methods to create and delete a namespace object. In this version, an Instance is an abstraction around a Kubernetes namespace.
